{"tid":2396680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恆江樓「唔使搵食呀?」「我有自由!」男女分別企圖逃離禁區被警員制服","createTime":"2021-02-05T20:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T02:39:50.000Z","uid":261647,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"b60f0181b0b157ae60d02d7ca6896c048456ae97","tid":2396680,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20:21:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photographicsocietyhk/posts/511355673596816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphotographicsocietyhk%2Fposts%2F511355673596816&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=867cb28f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photographicsocietyhk/posts/511355673596816</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tq4PEgF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftq4PEgF.png&h=7c701e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：PSHK<br />\n<br />\n【5/2 恆江樓「唔使搵食呀?」「我有自由!」男女分別企圖逃離禁區被警員制服】<br />\n<br />\n晚上10時，恆江樓 檢 測 站有一名男子到 檢 測站時突然情緒激動，與在場警員爭論，其間一度大喊「我有自由!」，隨後企圖逃離禁區，最少5名警員追前及將其挾返禁區內，有警員按撫其情緒。<br />\n<br />\n約11時，另一名女士疑因需要上班而企圖跳上花糟逃離禁區，有女警員隨即上前將其制伏於花糟旁位置，其間該名女士一度大叫「唔使搵食呀?」。其後有工作人員上前了解。<br />\n<br />\n封鎖其間有不少居民對封區非常不滿，更於接受傳媒訪問鏡頭前大罵香港特首林鄭月娥及建制派人士。"},{"pid":"c9f447d46291db5a02dc15b1278eebfa969d8ba6","tid":2396680,"uid":316747,"like":38,"dislike":15,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20:26:36.000Z","msg":"香港人返工既決心幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dd6055eacf2959839f692dea98215da9451b62","tid":2396680,"uid":8014,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20:28:02.000Z","msg":"黎生黎太<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c775e795d4256c7d41f773d25560516baa0ec9","tid":2396680,"uid":325346,"like":32,"dislike":5,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20: